</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-gFmZvT eCWkjm pf-65_ pf-text-1"><strong>Tailored training programs</strong> - Adapting training to address the specific risks and needs identified through risk assessments in the educational environment.













</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-gFmZvT eCWkjm pf-67_ pf-text-1"><strong>Integration of mental health first aid</strong> - Including training that addresses mental health crises, recognising their growing prevalence in further education settings.













